cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this benchmark or the accompanying paper, please cite as below."
title: "Agent Brain Benchmarks"
abstract: >
  Public, reproducible evaluation code for Agent Brain on LongMemEval, including
  ingestion scripts, retrieval variants (Brain with Dream Cycle, Brain without
  consolidation, pgvector-only baseline), and GPT-4o judge. Companion code to
  the paper "Agent Brain: A Biologically Inspired Memory System for Autonomous
  AI Agents, with Head-to-Head Evaluation on LongMemEval".
